safeties:
   when draining or filling begin, allow only some max time before transitioning to IDLE, or to ERROR




IDLE  ---[TopWentHigh]--->  DRAINING  ---[BottomWentLow]--->  FILLING  ---[TopIsHigh]-->  IDLE
                               |                                 |
                               |                                 |
                            [TooSlow]                        [TooSlow]
                               |                                 |
                               |                                 |
                               \--------->  ERROR  <-------------/


